INTRODUCTION: THE PURPOSE OF PHYSICAL REALITY

Crossing New Thresholds

• In 2023, humanity is crossing a threshold in more ways than one
• Starting slowly but definitely moving forward
• This transmission addresses the fundamental question: Why are you here in physical reality?

Common Challenges with Physical Reality

• Many people have many challenges with physical reality as an experience
• Many yearn to connect more strongly with spirit (or at least feel the connection more strongly)
• The key is to remember: You CHOSE to have this physical experience
• You chose it for your own purposes, for your own growth

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

THE NATURE OF PHYSICAL REALITY

Physical Reality as Densification of Spirit

• Physical reality is as dense as it is because it is:
  - A densification of spiritual energy
  - A crystallization of spiritual energy
  - A projection of consciousness
  - Not a place unto itself exactly
  - Going on within your awareness

The Purpose of Dense Physical Reality

• The density exists for the purpose of exploring and examining things in a different way
• A different time frame that allows you the opportunity to discover:
  - New aspects of yourself
  - New perspectives of yourself
• Physical reality has been mentioned many times for this purpose of self-discovery

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

BENEFITS OF CHOOSING PHYSICAL EXPERIENCE

Personal Growth as a Soul

• Choosing to experience physical reality has many benefits
• You can take advantage of these for your own personal growth:
  - As a soul
  - As a being
  - As an aspect of all that is
  - As a reflection of the infinite

The Power of Staying in Positive Frameworks

• By learning to stay within:
  - Positive frameworks
  - Positive belief systems
  - Positive outlook
  - Positive expression
  - Positive actions

• Energetically speaking, you can experience many wondrous things
• Exploring physical reality in that state of being, in that energy allows you to:
  - Experience the process of change in a way that enhances your understanding
  - Enhance your ability in the future
  - Grow for yourself
  - Aid and assist others
