Building Your Repertoire

• By becoming familiar with all the different kinds of challenges you can have while experiencing physical reality
• It gives you a REPERTOIRE
• It gives you a LIBRARY to aid and assist other beings who may not be as familiar with that experience
• You become LIVING EXAMPLES of how to navigate the idea of physical reality

