THE IMPORTANCE OF MASTERING LIMITATIONS

For Present and Future

• It is very important not only for your present experience but also for the future of your planet
• More and more of you must truly learn to master the so-called limitations:
  - That you have created
  - That you've set up for yourselves
  - The challenges you've set up for yourselves while experiencing physical reality

Transmitting Your Mastery

• Master the limitations and transmit that experience, that mastery to others
• In your own words
• Understand the principles upon which you have agreed to play this game with each other

Understanding Consensus Reality

• Understand to what degree you are following the consensus reality
• Understand to what degree you can allow yourself to move in your own individual direction
