IMAGINATION, CREATIVITY, AND TRANSFORMATION

Allowing Full Creative Play

• Allow your imagination, your creativity to come into full play
• Apply that creativity to every experience in your physical reality
• Truly transform your awareness, your understanding of your relationship to all that is
• Allow all that is to experience all that it can be through the idea of new experiences

The Uniqueness of Experience

• Even though everything exists, it is the EXPERIENCE, the RELATIONSHIP, the PERSPECTIVES that are new
• Every single one of you is unique - a unique expression of all that is
• This holds true in physical reality as well, even more so in a sense

