WHAT PHYSICAL REALITY OFFERS THAT SPIRIT CANNOT

The Unique Advantages of Physical Reality

• You can do so many more things in physical reality than you can do in spirit
• This may seem like a contradiction because spirit allows you to experience:
  - Greater things
  - Different things
  - Broader things
  - More expansive things perhaps than in physical reality

The Paradox Explained

• But physical reality has UNIQUE THINGS that cannot be experienced in spirit
• Your ability to utilize space and time, the framework you have created in which to experience this concept of physical reality in your consciousness

Physical Reality as a Musical Instrument

• Space and time can be played like a musical instrument in many ways
• You can create:
  - New orchestrations
  - New understandings
  - New relationships of space and time within your consciousness
• That will create beautiful music within all that is
• Beautiful new perspectives within all that is

Physical Reality as an Art Form

• This is an ART FORM - physical reality
• You can learn to master it by following the idea of the formula, the cosmic compass
• There are ways in which you can understand how you are agreeing to play by the game of physical reality
• Play it in your way - uniquely, harmoniously, beautifully

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

TAKING ADVANTAGE OF THIS GIFT

Physical Reality as Opportunity

• Take advantage of this opportunity - it is a GIFT
• No matter how challenging it may seem at times
• No matter how dark it may seem at times
• No matter how negative it may seem at times
• Mastering this has everything to do with how you define your relationship to it

Allowing Challenges to Serve You

• Allow the challenges that come up in your life to be there for a reason - YOUR reason
• Really let go of any negative reflection of these ideas
• Know that even though you may recognize objectively that something may have been created from a negative space
• None of that has anything at all to do with how you will experience the effects of it in your life

Becoming a Living Example

• Become a living example of how to master and transform limitation into freedom
• Not only for yourself but for others as well
• Many others need these abilities
• Many others need to see in all of you that are willing to do so how such things can be transformed to positive effect

