BEING PRESENT IN PHYSICAL REALITY

The Power of Presence

• Be present in this physical reality
• Do not worry about the past
• Do not worry about the future
• Physical reality only exists in the PRESENT
• Just like everything, be in it right now

How to Be Present

• Be in it as fully as you can be
• As boldly as you can be
• As lovingly as you can be
• Be present and act from that presence

